title: #92Noon at The Fair!  Micheletti/ Johnson/ Burns
description: Live from the MN State Fair, Nordo is in for PA and joined by Pat Micheletti from 9-10 for some in-depth MN hockey talk, Ron Johnson hangs out from 10-11 with plenty of Vikings & Gophers football discussion, & Ryan Burns continues the Gophers football talk from 11-12!
